This update includes several new features and several improvements : New style: Overload Control video playback speed Change the order of effect layers by dragging and dropping them into the desired position Organize the effects and place the ones you use most in the first positions Now you can also rearrange custom styles saved by you in a more efficient way Choose the Organize option in the styles menu Import multiple saved styles at the same time Fixed an issue that prevented some users from being able to export 4K videos on newer devices Fixed an issue with the Scanner effect Interface improvements Error correction If you liked our app don t forget to rate it in the store :

This is a major update that includes many new features and improvements : New Style: Overload Change the playback speed when working with imported videos the global effect speed has been renamed to Effect Speed to avoid confusion Reorder effects on the layer stack by dragging and dropping them on the desired position Advanced mode Reorganize effects from the effect library the ones listed under the magic wand icon placing those you use the most on the first slots for example You can also reorganize and or delete your custom styles in a more efficient way tap on the big plus icon and choose the option Organize Import several styles at once Fixed a critical bug that would prevent some users from exporting videos in 4K when using newer devices Fixed a problem that would cause the Slit Scan effect not to work properly on some intensity levels UI Improvements Minor bug fixes If you enjoy using our app please consider leaving a review in the App Store :

New style: Electron New effect: Grid New options have been added to the following effects: Scanner No. 7 No. 8 Ripple No. 10 Collage No. 7 No.8 No. 9 Symmetry No. 7 Scanner effect has been improved and it is now possible to add it to photos too. Remember that this effect needs movement to work properly. Maximum duration for animated images has been increased to 5 minutes Maximum bitrate has been increased to 200Mbps The app will now show a warning if the estimated video size is larger than the available space on the device. Fixed errors in the Mask tool Interface improvements Error correction If you liked our app don t forget to rate it in the store :

We are happy to announce a new update! Control effect parameters over time Advanced mode only : Tap the circle next to the parameter to choose how it changes. It is possible to change the speed and curve of the animation sine wave ramp etc. . For example you can choose how the intensity of an effect fluctuates over time Choose the portion of the video that each effect will be applied to Advanced Mode only : Tap the clock icon next to the effect name to choose the portion to which the effect will be applied Videos are now saved at the same frame rate as the original video 30 60 FPS etc. Choose the frame rate 30 60 120 or 240 FPS when exporting animated images Tool for saving GIFs has been improved and corrected: The frame duration parameter works more accurately now New effect Depth is available for images with depth data photos taken in Portrait Mode . You can import a second image to use as a depth map or let the app generate an estimated map if the original image does not have depth data. When working with videos the app will always generate an approximate map New options have been added to the following effects: Ripple No. 7 No. 8 No. 9 Dissolve No. 5 No. 6 Scanner No. 6 New color filter: X Ray Use depth data as a mask by selecting the Import option and then Depth Map when using the Mask effect. Mask effect now supports grayscale: It is possible to select different areas of the image with different intensities for better control of the effects Scanner effect has been improved Fixed a bug that occasionally caused temporary files to take up a lot of space Interface improvements Bug fixes If you like our app don t forget to rate it in the store :

This update brings a wide range of new features! Enjoy : New styles: 1 bit Perception Old Tape New option has been added to the Pixelar effect No. 5 New effect: Interference New overlays: Noise 1 2 Save videos in 4K when working in image mode or video mode Available on the following devices: iPhone XS and newer iPad 8th generation and newer Apply effects to a selected part of the video When saving choose to save only the selected part or save the entire video in which only the selected part will have the effects. Choose the video format in which you want to save your projects: H.264 HEVC or Motion JPEG MJPEG Maximum bitrate has been increased to 100 Mbit s Choose whether to save the video with or without the original audio if the imported media is a video Export a video snippet as a GIF of up to 30 frames GIFs are now imported as video instead of a still image Pixel Effect No. 3 has been adjusted higher level means less pixelation now 8 bit style has been slightly modified Optimized for iOS 15 Interface improvements Fixed a bug that occasionally prevented users from saving videos Fixed a bug where global speed was not saved in custom styles Various other bug fixes If you liked our app don t forget to rate it in the store :

This feature does not necessarily change the video playback speed. 6 new styles: Artifacts Fire Video Game Fluid Cyborg Monitor New effect: Softness New options have been added to effects: Surreal N. 9 Collage N. 6 Dissolve N.3 N. 4 Datamosh N. 8 N. 9 9 new color filters Random Mode: Generate a random combination of effects with just one tap New option that allows you to hide layers You can now pause the animation before exporting as an image. This way you can preview the image before saving it. Disable all effects with just one tap in Classic Mode Datamosh Effect No. 4 has been improved: Minimum block size has been reduced Interface improvements Fixed a bug that affected the Plasma effect on some devices Fixed another bug that prevented the ASCII effect from working correctly in Classic mode Various other bug fixes If you like our app don t forget to rate it in the store :

Maximum resolution for exporting photos has been increased on some devices Import and export your styles: it is now possible to export the styles you created all at once or each one individually press for a few seconds on the style to export it New effects: Contour Oscillation Collage New styles: High Frequency Abstract New color filter: Retro New overlays: Particles Bokeh Digital Cosmo Vaporwave New options have been added: Color No. 7 No. 12 Surreal No. 8 Glass No. 7 No. 8 Lens No. 6 and Swirl No. 4 No. 5 Color Effect now has 3 controls: Intensity Speed Channel Control character size in ASCII effect New controls have been added to the Overlay effect: Color Saturation and Colorize Analog Effect No. 6 has been slightly modified as it is now possible to add vertical oscillation separately Swirl Effect No. 3 has been improved Size control has been improved and renamed to Speed Pixel Sorting Effect Maximum scrolling speed has been increased Motion Effect Text size has been normalized so that it now always appears to be the same size regardless of the resolution chosen Text Effect Full screen option has been added to camera mode Optimized for iOS 13 Interface improvements Error correction If you liked our app don t forget to rate it in the store :

Save your edited photos as animated GIFs! Video settings can now be found by selecting the export video icon no longer the tool icon Interface improvements Error correction If you liked our app don t forget to rate it in the store! :

You can now control the position of each layer individually in the final composition and add the same effect more than once. This advanced feature opens up a world of possibilities for your creations! Version 2.0 brings many new features: Masks: you can now choose which areas of the image video are affected by filters 3 novos estilos: Bad VHS Plasma and Binary 7 novos efeitos: Pixel Sorting Melt Glass ASCII Swirl Clone and Blend 2 novos ajustes: Sharpen and Hue Rad Effect No.6 is now a separate effect Stripes A new Motion control has been added to the effects tab this replaces the old Movement control New options added to effects: Analog Noise No. 5 Digital Noise No. 5 No. 6 Datamosh No. 5 No. 6 No. 7 Color No. 4 Dope No. 7 Rad No. 7 Ripple No. 4 No. 5 Quantization No. 3 A new parameter has been added to the Datamosh effect: It is now possible to change the block size The Real Glitch function has been improved The Symmetry effect has been improved The maximum value of the Offset parameter in the Chroma Shift effect has been increased Interface improvements Error correction If you liked our app don t forget to rate it on the App Store :
